    "40852117": {
      "title": "The effect of dentin desensitizer on shear bond strength of conventional and self-adhesive resin luting cements after aging",
      "abstract": "Clinical Relevance Following tooth preparation, application of Gluma Desensitizer does not impair the bond strength of conventional resin luting cements with etch-and-rinse adhesive systems and self-adhesive cements. Based on bond strength data and failure types observed, use of Gluma Desensitizer cannot be advised before cementation with Panavia 21."
